<view class="content data-v-3bbe5a99"><view class="data-v-3bbe5a99">Vuex可以用来做全局状态管理。
		而此例子是演示将当前登录用户信息存入Vuex，以便于在其他页面中也能直接渲染或获取用户信息</view><view style="margin-top:10rpx;" class="data-v-3bbe5a99">说明:<view style="margin-top:10rpx;" class="data-v-3bbe5a99">1、<text class="data-v-3bbe5a99">$user</text>对应 store/modules 目录下的js文件<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>以下两个方式均可以对 vuex 数据进行操作<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view><view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>方式一：<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>获取 Vuex 数据：<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>vk.getVuex('$user.userInfo')<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>更新 Vuex 数据：<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>vk.setVuex('$user.userInfo.avatar', avatar)<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view><view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>方式二：<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>获取 Vuex 数据：<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>vk.vuex.get('$user.userInfo')<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>更新 Vuex 数据：<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>vk.vuex.set('$user.userInfo.avatar', avatar);<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>触发 Vuex action：<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view>vk.vuex.dispatch('$user/addFootprint', data);<view class="_br data-v-3bbe5a99"></view></view></view><block wx:if="{{$root.g0}}"><view style="color:red;margin-top:10rpx;font-size:36rpx;" class="data-v-3bbe5a99">{{'当前登录用户：'+$root.g1+''}}<image style="width:70rpx;height:70rpx;border-radius:50%;" src="{{$root.g2}}" mode="aspectFill" class="data-v-3bbe5a99"></image></view></block><view style="margin-top:20rpx;" class="data-v-3bbe5a99"><input type="text" placeholder="用户名/邮箱/手机号" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','username','$event',[]],['form1']]]]]}}" value="{{form1.username}}" bindinput="__e" class="data-v-3bbe5a99"/><input type="text" password="true" placeholder="密码" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','password','$event',[]],['form1']]]]]}}" value="{{form1.password}}" bindinput="__e" class="data-v-3bbe5a99"/><button type="default" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['register',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e" class="data-v-3bbe5a99">注册</button><button type="default" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['login',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e" class="data-v-3bbe5a99">登录</button><button type="default" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['uploadAvatar',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e" class="data-v-3bbe5a99">上传到云储存(并设置为头像)</button><button type="default" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['logout',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e" class="data-v-3bbe5a99">退出</button></view></view>